		"con": "<section id=\"content\"><p>2016-09-21</p><header><img alt=\"\" src=\"/wisdom/images/news/con19-1.jpg\" /></header><article></article><header><h1>獎學金如何申請?</h1><img alt=\"\" class=\"left\" src=\"/wisdom/images/news/con19-2.jpg\" /></header><article><p> &nbsp;</p><p> 凡透過捷先申請伯明翰城市大學，<strong><a href=\"http://www.getsetglobal.com.tw/schools/birmingham-city-university\">伯明翰城市大學</a></strong>將提供2017一月份入學新生獎學金 &pound;1,500 (除ACCA課程以外)</p></article><header><h1>加碼送很大</h1><img alt=\"\" class=\"right\" src=\"/wisdom/images/news/con19-3.jpg\" /></header><article><p> &nbsp;</p><p> 凡透過捷先申請伯明翰城市大學，捷先再加碼贈送伯明翰單程機票一張</p><p> ※學生需申請成功並繳交學費訂金</p></article><header><h1>伯明翰城市大學秋季班有什麼課程可以選擇?</h1><img alt=\"\" class=\"left\" src=\"/wisdom/images/news/con19-4.jpg\" /></header><article><p> &nbsp;</p><p> 課程涵蓋商學，法律，藝術與設計，電腦與工程，大學，碩士，博班，一年學費不到50萬台幣</p><table class=\"table table-striped\"><colgroup><col /><col /></colgroup><tbody><tr><td><strong>Business School Programmes</strong></td><td> Fees</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://www.bcu.ac.uk/courses/acca-ft\">ACCA (Full-time)&nbsp;- &pound;950 per module&nbsp;</a></td><td> 3,800 - 5,700</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://www.bcu.ac.uk/courses/business-admin-top-up\">BA (Hons) Business Administration (Top-Up)</a></td><td> 12,000</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://www.bcu.ac.uk/courses/mba\">MBA International (15 months)</a></td><td> 14,500</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://www.bcu.ac.uk/courses/management-and-finance-msc\">MSc Management and Finance</a></td><td> 12,000</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://www.bcu.ac.uk/courses/management-and-international-business-msc\">MSc Management and International Business</a></td><td> 12,000</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://www.bcu.ac.uk/courses/business-phd-research-degrees\">Research to PhD (Business)</a></td><td> 12,000 per year</td></tr><tr><td style=\"height:22px;width:603px;\"><strong>Law</strong></td><td> &nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://www.bcu.ac.uk/courses/international-business-law\">LLM International Business Law</a></td><td> 12,000</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://www.bcu.ac.uk/courses/international-human-rights\">LLM International Human Rights</a></td><td> 12,000</td></tr><tr><td style=\"height:22px;width:603px;\"><strong>Art and Design</strong></td><td> &nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://www.bcu.ac.uk/courses/contemporary-arts-china\">MA Contemporary Arts China</a></td><td> 12,000</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://www.bcu.ac.uk/courses/international-jewellery-business-ba-hons\">BA (Hons) International Jewellery Business</a></td><td> 12,000 per year</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://www.bcu.ac.uk/courses/jewellery-silversmithing-and-related-products-gradcert\">Graduate Certificate: Jewellery, Silversmithing and Related Products (Pre-MA)</a></td><td> 7,250</td></tr><tr><td style=\"height:22px;width:603px;\"><strong>Computing, Engineering &amp; the Built Envirnoment</strong></td><td> &nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://www.bcu.ac.uk/courses/computer-science-msc\">MSc Computer Science</a></td><td> 12,000</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://www.bcu.ac.uk/courses/environmental-sustainability-pgcert-pgdip-msc\">MSc Environmental Sustainability (Strategy and Management)</a></td><td> 12,000</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://www.bcu.ac.uk/courses/logistics\">MSc Logistics and Supply Chain Management</a></td><td> 12,000</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://www.bcu.ac.uk/courses/project-management\">MSc Project Management</a></td><td> 12,000</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://www.bcu.ac.uk/courses/construction-project-management\">MSc Construction Project Management</a></td><td> 12,000</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://www.bcu.ac.uk/courses/planning-built-and-natural-environments-ma\">MA Planning Built and Natural Environments</a></td><td> 12,000</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://bcu.ac.uk/courses/quantity-surveying-msc\">MSc Quantity Surveying</a></td><td> 12,000</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://bcu.ac.uk/courses/msc-building-surveying\">MSc Building Surveying</a></td><td> 12,000</td></tr><tr><td style=\"height:22px;width:603px;\"><strong>English Preparatory Courses</strong></td><td> &nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://www.bcu.ac.uk/international/your-application/english-language-and-english-tests/pre-sessional-english-courses\">November Pre-sessional English (10 weeks)</a></td><td> 3,000</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://www.bcu.ac.uk/international/your-application/english-language-and-english-tests/pre-sessional-english-courses\">December Pre-sessional English (6 weeks)</a></td><td> 1,800</td></tr></tbody></table><p> &nbsp;</p></article><header><h1>語言成績不到怎麼辦?</h1></header><article><p> 放心，你依然可以提前去上語言課程，免去在台灣掙扎的痛苦</p><p> 語言先修10周(與目標成績相差一分)</p><p> Monday 10 October 2016 - Friday 16 December 2016</p><p> &pound;3,000</p><p> 語言先修6周(與目標成績相差0.5分)</p><p> Monday 7 November 2016 - Friday 16 December 2016</p><p> &pound;1,800</p><p> 時間緊迫，同學們動作要快唷!!!</p><p> 想了解更多資訊，<strong><a href=\"/wisdom/contact.html?name=inlineBox\">歡迎洽詢捷先留學中心</a></strong></p><p> 捷先各辦公室: 02 2778 1595 / 04 2305 5785 / 06 302 5951 / 07 726 3525</p></article></section>"
